  "title": "Enum PixelFormat",
  "content": "<h1 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelFormat' data-commentId='T:Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelFormat' id='Alis_Core_Graphic_OpenGL_Enums_PixelFormat'>Enum PixelFormat    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Graphic/src/OpenGL/Enums/PixelFormat.cs#L35'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h1>\r\n <div class=\"facts text-secondary\">\r\n<dl><dt>Namespace</dt><dd><a href='Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.html'>Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums</a></dd></dl><dl><dt>Assembly</dt><dd>Alis.dll</dd></dl>\r\n</div><p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelFormat.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The pixel format enum</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public enum PixelFormat</code></pre><h2 class='section'>Fields</h2><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>ColorIndex = 6400</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelFormat.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The color index pixel format</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>StencilIndex = 6401</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelFormat.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The stencil index pixel format</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>DepthComponent = 6402</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelFormat.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The depth component pixel format</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>Red = 6403</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelFormat.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The red pixel format</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>Green = 6404</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelFormat.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The green pixel format</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>Blue = 6405</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelFormat.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The blue pixel format</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>Alpha = 6406</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelFormat.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The alpha pixel format</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>Rgb = 6407</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelFormat.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The rgb pixel format</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>Rgba = 6408</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelFormat.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The rgba pixel format</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>Luminance = 6409</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelFormat.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The luminance pixel format</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>LuminanceAlpha = 6410</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelFormat.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The luminance alpha pixel format</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>AbgrExt = 32768</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelFormat.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The abgr ext pixel format</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>CmykExt = 32780</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelFormat.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The cmyk ext pixel format</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>CmykaExt = 32781</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelFormat.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The cmyka ext pixel format</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>Bgr = 32992</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelFormat.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The bgr pixel format</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>Bgra = 32993</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelFormat.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The bgra pixel format</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>Ycrcb422Sgix = 33211</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelFormat.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The ycrcb 422 sgix pixel format</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>Ycrcb444Sgix = 33212</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelFormat.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The ycrcb 444 sgix pixel format</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>Rg = 33319</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelFormat.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The rg pixel format</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>RgInteger = 33320</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelFormat.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The rg integer pixel format</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>DepthStencil = 34041</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelFormat.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The depth stencil pixel format</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>RedInteger = 36244</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelFormat.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The red integer pixel format</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>GreenInteger = 36245</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelFormat.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The green integer pixel format</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>BlueInteger = 36246</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelFormat.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The blue integer pixel format</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>AlphaInteger = 36247</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelFormat.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The alpha integer pixel format</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>RgbInteger = 36248</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelFormat.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The rgb integer pixel format</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>RgbaInteger = 36249</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelFormat.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The rgba integer pixel format</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>BgrInteger = 36250</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelFormat.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The bgr integer pixel format</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>BgraInteger = 36251</code>   </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Graphic.OpenGL.Enums.PixelFormat.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The bgra integer pixel format</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl>",
